Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE Limited is pleased to present this rare and exciting opportunity to lease or purchase two ground floor, corner lot, retail units located at 112 & 114 Carrie Cates Court in North Vancouver, British Columbia. Conveniently located across from the Lonsdale Quay, this new development capitalizes on local shoppers and tourists due to its stunning picturesque views and countless amenities. These two units have a maximum ceiling height of 16’3”, substantial electrical power, venting and grease trap capabilities, and access to commercial loading and garbage. The two units can either be leased or purchased together or separately. Promenade is a 14 storey, concrete development built by Polygon, with 117 residential units above, 81 underground customer parking stalls (mix of paid parking and dedicated stalls), and two grade-level loading bays.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FOR SALE/LEASE | TOP-TIER RETAIL UNITS IN THE HEART OF LOWER LONSDALE
